==Historical district boundaries==

From 2003 to 2013, the 19th district was based in South Florida. The district included parts of [[Palm Beach County, Florida|Palm Beach]] and [[Broward County, Florida|Broward]] counties, including the cities of [[Coral Springs, Florida|Coral Springs]], [[Margate, Florida|Margate]], and [[Greenacres, Florida|Greenacres]].

